{"type":"message","id":"8bb0ab09","parentId":"9dffbd99","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:40:40.219Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"5910\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khuong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 10:40 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khuong (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khuong\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nCheck xem frontend gửi ở trong student detail chỗ thêm buổi dat đang gửi lên những field gì"}],"timestamp":1776940840187}}
{"type":"message","id":"896c652b","parentId":"8bb0ab09","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:40:55.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mình kiểm tra đúng component “Student Detail → thêm buổi DAT” rồi đối chiếu payload FE đang gửi lên."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_30fq6dQ33wA0dNJB6WjewOFU","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx","offset":1,"limit":180}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_noSQ42f9xB5vPlzG9TUuX77Z","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx","offset":500,"limit":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_JGv6sde1eiC4ZQCGtaHeh9Ef","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/datService.ts","offset":1,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":2285,"output":258,"cacheRead":71040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73583,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776940840225,"responseId":"1776940842265"}}
{"type":"message","id":"74cc62cd","parentId":"896c652b","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:40:55.736Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_30fq6dQ33wA0dNJB6WjewOFU","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import React, { useState } from 'react';\nimport ViDateInput from '@/src/components/shared/ViDateInput';\nimport { X, Calendar, Clock, MapPin, Save, Loader2 } from 'lucide-react';\nimport { toast } from 'sonner';\nimport { addDatSession } from '@/src/services/datService';\n\ninterface DatSessionModalProps {\n  isOpen: boolean;\n  onClose: () => void;\n  enrollmentId: string;\n  onSuccess: () => void;\n}\n\nconst DatSessionModal: React.FC<DatSessionModalProps> = ({ isOpen, onClose, enrollmentId, onSuccess }) => {\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\n  const [formData, setFormData] = useState({\n    date: new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0],\n    startTime: '08:00',\n    endTime: '10:00',\n    duration: '120', // Default 120 minutes (2 hours)\n    distance: '',\n    notes: '',\n  });\n\n  const syncDuration = (startStr: string, endStr: string) => {\n    try {\n      const [sh, sm] = startStr.split(':').map(Number);\n      const [eh, em] = endStr.split(':').map(Number);\n      const diffMinutes = eh * 60 + em - (sh * 60 + sm);\n      return Math.max(0, diffMinutes).toString();\n    } catch {\n      return '0';\n    }\n  };\n\n  const syncEndTime = (startStr: string, durationStr: string) => {\n    try {\n      const [sh, sm] = startStr.split(':').map(Number);\n      const totalMinutes = sh * 60 + sm + parseInt(durationStr || '0');\n      const eh = Math.floor(totalMinutes / 60) % 24;\n      const em = totalMinutes % 60;\n      return `${eh.toString().padStart(2, '0')}:${em.toString().padStart(2, '0')}`;\n    } catch {\n      return startStr;\n    }\n  };\n\n  if (!isOpen) return null;\n\n  const handleSubmit = async (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!formData.distance || isNaN(parseFloat(formData.distance))) {\n      toast.error('Vui lòng nhập quãng đường hợp lệ.');\n      return;\n    }\n    if (!formData.duration || isNaN(parseInt(formData.duration))) {\n      toast.error('Vui lòng nhập số phút học hợp lệ.');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    setLoading(true);\n    try {\n      const start = new Date(`${formData.date}T${formData.startTime}:00`);\n      const end = new Date(`${formData.date}T${formData.endTime}:00`);\n\n      if (end <= start) {\n        toast.error('Thời gian kết thúc phải sau thời gian bắt đầu.');\n        setLoading(false);\n        return;\n      }\n\n      const res = await addDatSession({\n        course_student_id: enrollmentId,\n        session_type: 'dat',\n        start_time: start.toISOString(),\n        end_time: end.toISOString(),\n        distance_km: parseFloat(formData.distance),\n        notes: formData.notes,\n      });\n\n      if (res.success) {\n        toast.success('Đã thêm buổi DAT thành công!');\n        onSuccess();\n        onClose();\n      } else {\n        toast.error(res.message || 'Có lỗi xảy ra.');\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      toast.error('Lỗi khi kết nối đến máy chủ.');\n    } finally {\n      setLoading(false);\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm animate-in fade-in duration-200\">\n      <div className=\"bg-white w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden animate-in zoom-in-95 duration-200\">\n        <div className=\"px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-100 flex justify-between items-center bg-indigo-50/30\">\n          <h3 className=\"font-black text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <div className=\"p-1.5 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 rounded-lg\">\n              <Clock className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </div>\n            Thêm buổi DAT mới\n          </h3>\n          <button onClick={onClose} className=\"p-2 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full transition-colors\">\n            <X className=\"w-5 h-5 text-gray-400\" />\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} className=\"p-6 flex flex-col gap-5\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n              <Calendar className=\"w-3 h-3\" /> Ngày học\n            </label>\n            <ViDateInput\n              required\n              value={formData.date}\n              onChange={(val) => setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, date: val }))}\n              className=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-600/20 text-sm font-medium\"\n            />\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5 p-4 bg-indigo-50/50 border border-indigo-100 rounded-2xl\">\n              <label className=\"text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-600 uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5 tracking-widest\">\n                <Clock className=\"w-3 h-3\" strokeWidth={3} /> Thời lượng học (Phút)\n              </label>\n              <div className=\"relative mt-1\">\n                <input\n                  type=\"number\"\n                  required\n                  min=\"1\"\n                  placeholder=\"VD: 120\"\n                  value={formData.duration}\n                  onChange={(e) => {\n                    const newDur = e.target.value;\n                    setFormData((prev) => ({\n                      ...prev,\n                      duration: newDur,\n                      endTime: syncEndTime(prev.startTime, newDur),\n                    }));\n                  }}\n                  className=\"w-full px-0 py-1 bg-transparent border-none focus:ring-0 text-2xl font-black text-indigo-600 placeholder:text-indigo-200\"\n                />\n                <span className=\"absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-xs font-bold text-indigo-400 uppercase\">phút</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 bg-gray-50/50 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n              <label className=\"text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5 tracking-widest\">\n                <Clock className=\"w-3 h-3\" /> Bắt đầu\n              </label>\n              <input\n                type=\"time\"\n                required\n                value={formData.startTime}\n                onChange={(e) => {\n                  const newStart = e.target.value;\n                  setFormData((prev) => ({\n                    ...prev,\n                    startTime: newStart,\n                    duration: syncDuration(newStart, prev.endTime),\n                  }));\n                }}\n                className=\"w-full bg-transparent border-none p-0 text-sm font-black text-gray-700 focus:ring-0\"\n              />\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5 border-l border-gray-200 pl-4\">\n              <label className=\"text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase flex items-center gap-1.5 tracking-widest\">\n                <Clock className=\"w-3 h-3\" /> Kết thúc\n              </label>\n              <input\n                type=\"time\"\n                required\n                value={formData.endTime}\n                onChange={(e) => {\n                  const newEnd = e.target.value;\n                  setFormData((prev) => ({\n\n[65 more lines in file. Use offset=181 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776940855729}}
{"type":"message","id":"231e0258","parentId":"74cc62cd","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:40:55.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_noSQ42f9xB5vPlzG9TUuX77Z","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n    const errs = validatePayment(paymentForm);\n    setPaymentErrors(errs);\n\n    if (Object.keys(errs).length > 0) {\n      toast.error('Vui lòng điền đầy đủ thông tin thanh toán!');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const courseStudentId = fullData?.enrollment?._id;\n    if (!courseStudentId) {\n      toast.error('Học viên chưa được đăng ký khóa học nào!');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    setIsSubmittingPayment(true);\n    try {\n      const stageMap: Record<string, string> = {\n        'Đăng ký ban đầu': 'tuition_fee',\n        'Học thực hành': 'practice_completed',\n        'Thi hết môn': 'graduation_exam',\n        'Thi sát hạch': 're_exam_fee',\n      };\n\n      const payload = {\n        course_student_id: courseStudentId,\n        payment_date: new Date(paymentForm.date).toISOString(),\n        type: stageMap[paymentForm.stage] || 'other',\n        is_received: true,\n        received_fee: Number(parseNumberFromDots(paymentForm.amount)),\n        note: paymentForm.receipt,\n        stage_name: paymentForm.stage,\n      };\n\n      let res;\n      if (editingPaymentId) {\n        res = await updatePayment(editingPaymentId, {\n          payment_date: payload.payment_date,\n          received_fee: payload.received_fee,\n          note: payload.note,\n          stage_name: payload.stage_name,\n        });\n      } else {\n        res = await createPayment(payload);\n      }\n\n      if (res.success) {\n        toast.success(\n          editingPaymentId\n            ? `Đã cập nhật lịch sử đóng tiền thành công!`\n            : `Đã ghi nhận đóng ${paymentForm.amount}đ thành công cho ${student.name}!`,\n        );\n\n        // Auto print\n        handlePrintPayment({\n          ...payload,\n          _id: editingPaymentId || res.data?._id || 'NEW',\n          payment_date: payload.payment_date,\n          received_fee: payload.received_fee,\n        });\n\n[1901 more lines in file. Use offset=560 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776940855738}}
{"type":"message","id":"118c738c","parentId":"231e0258","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:40:55.753Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_JGv6sde1eiC4ZQCGtaHeh9Ef","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { apiClient } from './api';\n\nexport interface DatSession {\n  _id?: string;\n  course_student_id: string;\n  session_type: 'cabin' | 'dat';\n  start_time: string;\n  end_time: string;\n  distance_km: number;\n  notes?: string;\n  created_at?: string;\n}\n\nexport const addDatSession = (data: Partial<DatSession>) => {\n  return apiClient('/dat', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    body: JSON.stringify(data),\n  });\n};\n\nexport const getStudentDatSessions = (enrollmentId: string) => {\n  return apiClient(`/dat/student/${enrollmentId}`);\n};\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776940855746}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7c4c339","parentId":"118c738c","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:41:18.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Trong **Student Detail → thêm buổi DAT**, frontend hiện đang gửi lên đúng các field này:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"course_student_id\": \"<enrollmentId>\",\n  \"session_type\": \"dat\",\n  \"start_time\": \"<ISO string>\",\n  \"end_time\": \"<ISO string>\",\n  \"distance_km\": <number>,\n  \"notes\": \"<string>\"\n}\n```\n\n**Cụ thể trong code**\nFile:\n- `src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx`\n\nĐoạn submit đang gọi:\n\n```ts\nconst res = await addDatSession({\n  course_student_id: enrollmentId,\n  session_type: 'dat',\n  start_time: start.toISOString(),\n  end_time: end.toISOString(),\n  distance_km: parseFloat(formData.distance),\n  notes: formData.notes,\n});\n```\n\n**Nguồn của từng field**\n- `course_student_id` = prop `enrollmentId`\n- `session_type` = hardcode `\"dat\"`\n- `start_time` = ghép từ `date + startTime` rồi convert `toISOString()`\n- `end_time` = ghép từ `date + endTime` rồi convert `toISOString()`\n- `distance_km` = `parseFloat(formData.distance)`\n- `notes` = `formData.notes`\n\n**Field có trên form nhưng KHÔNG gửi lên**\n- `date`\n- `startTime`\n- `endTime`\n- `duration`\n\nTức là `duration` chỉ dùng để tính UI/time helper, **không được submit lên backend**.\n\nNếu bạn muốn, mình có thể làm tiếp bước kế:\n1. so payload này với **model DAT/backend thực tế**\n2. chỉ ra chỗ nào **thiếu field / sai field / sai logic**\n3. fix luôn cho bạn."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":4747,"output":384,"cacheRead":71168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76299,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776940855761,"responseId":"1776940857485"}}
