{"type":"compaction","id":"42a8ea97","parentId":"90920ff5","timestamp":"2026-04-23T11:08:16.075Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Fix issues in the AHV QLHV projects (`ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-qlhv-be`) according to user requests, with branch-per-task and commit-only workflow.\n- Current active goal: apply the same “disable add DAT when no enrollment/course_student_id” logic from Student Detail to the DAT Progress page.\n- Earlier goals in this session also included:\n  - Diagnose/fix health check update persistence.\n  - Fix Student Detail DAT button behavior.\n  - Fix add-student form sync between course and license rank.\n  - Investigate/report portal back-link issue (assistant fixed the wrong location; user said that was not the real issue).\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Always use prompt-optimizer first to clarify, then confirm with user, then implement.\n- Do not type code directly unless via workflow/agent when possible; user preference says use spawn agent workflow.\n- Must **checkout a new branch before doing work**.\n- Must **not push**.\n- Only **commit** after finishing.\n- Local only agent ecosystem, no GitLab push.\n- MongoDB only, no PostgreSQL.\n- User language preference: Vietnamese.\n- User explicitly asked after fixes to run project for UI testing when relevant.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Confirmed correct project paths:\n  - `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be`\n  - `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n- [x] Diagnosed/fixed backend health check persistence issue in `ahv-qlhv-be`.\n  - Branch: `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423`\n  - Commit: `46afadc` — `fix: persist health check update without existing enrollment`\n  - File changed: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/student.service.ts`\n  - Core fix: in `needsEnrollmentUpdate` path, if no latest enrollment exists but a course can be resolved, create minimal `CourseStudent` and persist `health_check`; otherwise throw:\n    - `Không thể cập nhật hồ sơ khám sức khỏe vì học viên chưa có khóa học/enrollment để lưu dữ liệu.`\n- [x] Built backend successfully:\n  - `npm run build` in BE passed.\n- [x] Attempted FE build; failed due unrelated repo issue:\n  - `./playwright.config.ts:1:39`\n  - `Type error: Cannot find module '@playwright/test' or its corresponding type declarations.`\n- [x] Ran FE dev server on port `3002`.\n- [x] Tried BE dev; first failed because env missing:\n  - `Missing MongoDB configuration: MONGODB_URI and MONGODB_NAME are required`\n- [x] Tried BE dev with `MONGODB_NAME=ahv_qlhv`; DB/seed env looked misconfigured and produced:\n  - `Invalid database name: 'ahv_qlhv/ahv_qlhv'`\n- [x] Investigated DAT model fields and FE payload.\n  - BE model: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/dat_session.model.ts`\n  - FE service: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/datService.ts`\n  - Student Detail modal payload from `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx` sends:\n    - `course_student_id`\n    - `session_type: 'dat'`\n    - `start_time`\n    - `end_time`\n    - `distance_km`\n    - `notes`\n- [x] Fixed Student Detail DAT button so user cannot add DAT when student has no enrollment.\n  - Branch: `fix/disable-dat-button-without-enrollment-20260423`\n  - Commit: `04de21c` — `fix: disable DAT add action without enrollment`\n  - File changed: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx`\n  - Behavior added:\n    - Disable button if `!fullData?.enrollment?._id`\n    - Tooltip/title:\n      - `Học viên chưa vào khóa, không thể thêm buổi DAT.`\n    - Inline UI message:\n      - `Học viên chưa vào khóa nên chưa thể thêm buổi DAT.`\n- [x] Fixed add-student form course/rank sync behavior.\n  - Branch: `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423`\n  - Commit: `963244c` — `fix: sync student course selection with license rank`\n  - File changed: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/AddStudentModal.tsx`\n  - Behavior now:\n    - When no rank selected, show all courses.\n    - When user selects a course, auto-map `rank = course.license_category_id`.\n    - When user manually changes rank and a course is already selected, clear `course`.\n    - Tuition recalculates only when not manually overridden.\n- [x] Fixed report portal back links, but user said: `Không phải lỗi ở đó`.\n  - Branch: `fix/report-portal-back-link-20260423`\n  - Commit: `932b4a1` — `fix: repair report portal back links`\n  - This was likely the wrong target for the user’s actual portal issue.\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] User asked: “Tiếp theo ở trang tiến độ DAT cũng cần xử lý logic giống phần theme dat trong student detail”\n- [ ] Assistant has clarified the intended change and is waiting for user confirmation:\n  - If no enrollment / `course_student_id`, disable add-DAT action on the DAT Progress page and show reason in UI.\n\n### Blocked\n- User confirmation pending for the DAT Progress page fix (`đúng, fix luôn` requested by assistant).\n- FE production build still blocked by existing repo issue:\n  - `Cannot find module '@playwright/test' or its corresponding type declarations.`\n- BE dev env is inconsistent:\n  - `.env` has `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/ahv_qlhv`\n  - code expects separate `MONGODB_URI` base + `MONGODB_NAME`\n  - setting `MONGODB_NAME=ahv_qlhv` caused `Invalid database name: 'ahv_qlhv/ahv_qlhv'`\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Health check data belongs to enrollment, not root student**: Root cause of “update success but not persisted” was backend enrollment-linked persistence logic.\n- **Student Detail DAT should be blocked at UI when no enrollment exists**: Prevent invalid add flow instead of relying on backend failure.\n- **Add Student form should auto-map rank from selected course**: User explicitly wants “Khi chưa chọn thì show tất cả khóa khi chọn một khóa tự động mapping hạng bằng”.\n- **Do not push any branch**: User explicitly forbade pushing; commit only.\n- **Create a fresh branch for each task**: Followed per user instruction even across FE/BE and docs tasks.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Wait for or infer user confirmation to proceed with DAT Progress page fix.\n2. In `ahv-qlhv-fe`, locate DAT Progress page/component add-session action (likely under `src/app/progress/page.tsx` and/or related DAT modal/component).\n3. Apply same gating as Student Detail:\n   - disable add button when missing enrollment / `course_student_id`\n   - prevent modal open/submit\n   - show clear UI message explaining why\n4. Commit on a new branch before changes if following user’s strict pattern again from current branch state.\n5. Optionally run FE dev for user testing after the change.\n\n## Critical Context\n- User identity/context from memory:\n  - Khuong / Khương Nịnh, prefers Vietnamese.\n- Relevant project paths:\n  - FE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n  - BE: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- Current/previous FE branches used this session:\n  - `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423`\n  - `fix/disable-dat-button-without-enrollment-20260423`\n  - `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423`\n- Current Student Detail DAT fix reference:\n  - `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/StudentDetailDrawer.tsx`\n  - It checks `fullData?.enrollment?._id` for enabling/disabling the DAT add button.\n- DAT FE payload reference:\n  - `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/components/students/modules/DatSessionModal.tsx`\n  - Uses `addDatSession({ course_student_id: enrollmentId, session_type: 'dat', start_time, end_time, distance_km, notes })`\n- DAT BE model required fields:\n  - `course_student_id`\n  - `session_type` (`'cabin' | 'dat'`)\n  - `start_time`\n  - `end_time`\n  - `distance_km`\n- Earlier wrong-path portal fix should not be treated as the actual user-requested portal bug.\n- Last user message:\n  - `Tiếp theo ở trang tiến độ DAT cũng cần xử lý logic giống phần theme dat trong student detail`\n- Last assistant message asked for confirmation instead of implementing.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\n- User asked to “fix it too” on the DAT progress page: specifically apply the same blocking/guard logic as in Student Detail when adding a DAT session.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Assistant confirmed the target was the DAT progress page and planned to find the “Thêm buổi” button and enforce the same guard as Student Detail.\n- Checked repo status and current branch:\n  - Current branch before work: `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423`\n- Searched relevant files and found:\n  - `src/components/progress/AddDatModal.tsx`\n  - `src/app/progress/page.tsx`\n- Noted from search results:\n  - `AddDatModal` accepts `enrollmentId?: string`\n  - Modal already checks `if (!enrollmentId)` internally\n  - API payload uses `course_student_id: enrollmentId`\n  - Progress page passes `enrollmentId={selectedStudentObj?.enrollment_id || selectedStudentObj?.enrollment?._id}`\n- Created a new branch for this fix:\n  - `fix/progress-dat-disable-without-enrollment-20260423`\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- The retained suffix contains code reads of:\n  - `src/app/progress/page.tsx` around the progress table/action area\n  - `src/components/progress/AddDatModal.tsx`\n- Important context:\n  - The bug/fix is about preventing DAT session creation when the student has no enrollment/course-student relation.\n  - `AddDatModal` already has backend-side/form-side protection via missing `enrollmentId`; likely remaining work is UI-level disable/hide/block on the progress page action button, matching Student Detail behavior.\n- The progress page is using selected student data with possible enrollment sources:\n  - `selectedStudentObj?.enrollment_id`\n  - `selectedStudentObj?.enrollment?._id`\n\n<